Here's the updated index.jsp file. I've added an inline style to the <section class="hero-section"> to include a doctor image in the background.

I've used a placeholder image URL for the doctor. If you have a specific image file for the doctor (e.g., in your /images/ folder), you can replace https://placehold.co/1200x600/609966/FFFFFF?text=Doctor+Image with your actual image path (e.g., /images/doctor_hero.jpg).

<%-- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/index.jsp --%>
<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" language="java" %>
